46. Apply All Assignment Operators
num = 100

print("Initial value:", num)

num += 20
print("After += 20:", num)

num -= 10
print("After -= 10:", num)

num *= 2
print("After *= 2:", num)

num /= 5
print("After /= 5:", num)

num %= 7
print("After %= 7:", num)

output:
Initial value: 100
After += 20: 120
After -= 10: 110
After *= 2: 220
After /= 5: 44.0
After %= 7: 2.0


